Hello! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides, the best bowling alley in town. My name is Alex, and I'll be happy to assist you today. May I know your name, please?

Hi Alex, my name is Jamie.

Nice to meet you, Jamie. How can I help you with billing today?

I'm trying to understand the charges on my last bill. It seems the amount is higher than usual.

I can certainly help with that. Could you please provide me with your billing account number for verification?

Sure, my billing account number is eight seven two one zero.

Thank you, Jamie. I see that there was an additional charge for a special event rental. Could you also confirm the last four digits of your phone number associated with the account?

The last four digits are three zero nine six.

Great, thank you for confirming that, Jamie. I see everything matches. The charge was indeed for the special event rental last Friday evening. Do you have any other questions regarding this?

No, that's all clear now. Thanks for your help, Alex.

You're welcome, Jamie. Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides. Have a wonderful day!
